sing age\nconspire to produce similar turnoff magnitudes and colors for all old clusters\nthat lie on the AMR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2011 21:02:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
