 phonon- paramagnon differential absorption processes.\nThe latter is enabled by a strong short-range in-plane spin correlations in the\nparamagnetic phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2011 10:26:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-02-13"}
